msgid "pre-commit 導入メモ"
msgstr "pre-commit implementation notes"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-16-pre-commit-introduction.rst:10
msgid ""
"本記事では、Git コミット前にコードやドキュメントの整形・チェックを自動で行うツール **pre-commit** "
"について、導入方法と活用を整理します"
msgstr ""
"In this article, we will explain how to introduce and utilize **pre-"
"commit**, a tool that automatically formats and checks code and documents "
"before committing to Git."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-16-pre-commit-introduction.rst:17
msgid "はじめに：pre-commit とは"
msgstr "Introduction: What is pre-commit?"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-16-pre-commit-introduction.rst:19
msgid ""
"`pre-commit` は、Git の「コミット前フック」を簡単に管理・運用するための Python 製ツールです。以下のような作業を自動化できます："
msgstr ""
"`pre-commit` is a Python tool for easily managing and operating Git's \"pre-"
"commit hooks\". You can automate tasks such as:"

