msgid "``doctoc``：Markdown の目次自動生成"
msgstr "``doctoc``: Markdown table of contents automatic generation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-16-pre-commit-introduction.rst:90
msgid "``mdformat``：Markdown の自動整形（Python製）"
msgstr "``mdformat``: Automatic formatting of Markdown (made in Python)"

