msgstr "``rstcheck``: Syntax validation for Sphinx"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-16-pre-commit-introduction.rst:94
msgid ""
"pre-commit で自動目次生成や API ドキュメント整形を行えば、**ドキュメントの陳腐化を防止** しつつ、**差分として明示できる** "
"のが大きな利点です。"
msgstr ""
"If you use pre-commit to automatically generate a table of contents and "
"format API documentation, the big advantage is that you can prevent "
"documents from becoming obsolete while also being able to show them as "
"differences."

